#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an10.80"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.80:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.80:0.2"
msgid "8. Ākaṅkhavagga "
msgstr "8. If You Want "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.80:0.3"
msgid "80. Āghātapaṭivinayasutta "
msgstr "80. Getting Rid of Resentment "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.151, sc1
msgctxt "an10.80:1.1"
msgid "“Dasayime, bhikkhave, āghātapaṭivinayā. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these ten methods to get rid of resentment. "

msgctxt "an10.80:1.2"
msgid "Katame dasa? "
msgstr "What ten? "

msgctxt "an10.80:1.3"
msgid "‘Anatthaṃ me acari, taṃ kutettha labbhā’ti āghātaṃ paṭivineti, "
msgstr "Thinking: ‘They harmed me, but what can I possibly do?’ you get rid of resentment. "

msgctxt "an10.80:1.4"
msgid "‘anatthaṃ me carati, taṃ kutettha labbhā’ti āghātaṃ paṭivineti, "
msgstr "Thinking: ‘They are harming me …’ … "

msgctxt "an10.80:1.5"
msgid "‘anatthaṃ me carissati, taṃ kutettha labbhā’ti āghātaṃ paṭivineti, "
msgstr "‘They will harm me …’ … "

msgctxt "an10.80:1.6"
msgid "piyassa me manāpassa anatthaṃ acari … pe … "
msgstr "‘They harmed someone I love …’ … "

msgctxt "an10.80:1.7"
msgid "carati … pe … "
msgstr "‘They are harming someone I love …’ "

msgctxt "an10.80:1.8"
msgid "carissati, taṃ kutettha labbhāti āghātaṃ paṭivineti, appiyassa me amanāpassa atthaṃ acari … pe … "
msgstr "‘They will harm someone I love …’ … They helped someone I dislike …’ … "

msgctxt "an10.80:1.9"
msgid "atthaṃ carati … pe … "
msgstr "‘They are helping someone I dislike …’ … "

msgctxt "an10.80:1.10"
msgid "atthaṃ carissati, taṃ kutettha labbhāti āghātaṃ paṭivineti, "
msgstr "Thinking: ‘They will help someone I dislike, but what can I possibly do?’ you get rid of resentment. "

msgctxt "an10.80:1.11"
msgid "aṭṭhāne ca na kuppati—"
msgstr "And you don’t get angry for no reason. "

msgctxt "an10.80:1.12"
msgid "ime kho, bhikkhave, dasa āghātapaṭivinayā”ti. "
msgstr "These are the ten ways of getting rid of resentment.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.80:1.13"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.80:1.14"
msgid "Ākaṅkhavaggo tatiyo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an10.80:2.1"
msgid "Ākaṅkho kaṇṭako iṭṭhā, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an10.80:2.2"
msgid "vaḍḍhi ca migasālāya; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an10.80:2.3"
msgid "Tayo dhammā ca kāko ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an10.80:2.4"
msgid "nigaṇṭhā dve ca āghātāti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
